      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、瑠依ちゃん見んかった？\n先にレッスン室行ったんかな？",
      "startTime": 4.1468748927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。今、会議室で雑誌の打ち合わせをしてるみたい\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の",
      "startTime": 12.206553189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやった、今日か！　アイドルのお願い聞いてくれる\nやつや。瑠依ちゃん、誕生日に何したいんやろ",
      "startTime": 18.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "何かな～。私だったら、やりたいこと\n沢山あって決められないよ～",
      "startTime": 27.4410824496,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3053.987372000002,
          "startTime": 30.4950698216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "待った？　打ち合わせが長引いちゃって",
      "startTime": 31.4291852634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "気にせんでええよ、まだレッスンまで時間あるし\nそれより、企画何にしたん？",
      "startTime": 39.9333361944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだけど……決まらなくて困ってるの\nやりたいことが全然思いつかないのよね",
      "startTime": 46.7827921709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあさ、一緒に考えない！？\n三人集まればなんとかの知恵って言うし。ね、優ちゃん",
      "startTime": 52.8494588376,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}